#+title: wagner group
#+filetags: :russia:

The Wagner Group
Russian: Группа Вагнера
Romanized: Gruppa Vagnera
Aliases: PMC Wagner, ChVK Wagner
(ChVK being the Russian abbreviation for Private Military Company

CHVK Vagner
ЧВК Вагнера ChVK Vagnera
Частная Военная Компания Вагнера

Russian paramilitary organization

Some have described it as a private military company
or private military contracting agency

whose contractors have reportedly taken part in various conflicts, including operations in the Syrian civil war on the side of the Syrian government as well as, from 2014 until 2015, in the war in Donbas in Ukraine aiding the separatist forces of the self-declared Donetsk and Luhansk people's republics.

ChVK Wagner as an arms-length unit of the Russian Ministry of Defence (MoD) and/or the GRU

Used by the Russian government in conflicts where deniability is called for.
Forces are trained on MoD installations.
It is believed to be owned by Yevgeny Prigozhin, a businessman with close links to Russian President Vladimir Putin. 
